O-O Nf5 13. Nxd5 Nxe3 14. Qxe3 $2 (14. Qxa5 Nxa5 15. Nxe3 cxd4 16. Nd5 {
is still more or less okay for White}) 14... cxd4 15. Ne7+ Nxe7 16. Qxe7 Qb6
17. Kh1 Qxb2 {and Black is just a pawn up, E.Mukhametzianova-O.Zimina,
