Krapivin-A.Kornev, Vladimir 2008.}) ({c)} 9... Nd4 10. Nh4 $5 Qa5 ({or} 10...
e5 11. f4 exf4 12. Bxf4 Ne7 13. O-O h6 14. Be3 g5 15. Nf3 Nxf3+ 16. Bxf3 Nc6
17. Bg2 Be6 18. a3 a5 19. axb4 axb4 20. c3 bxc3 21. bxc3 Ne5 {and a draw was
