c3 $6 bxc3 14. bxc3 Nc2 15. Ne2 Nxe3 16. Qxe3 Bd7 {is good for Black}) 13...
Qc7 14. f4 Nh6 15. h3 f5 16. Bf2 O-O 17. Ne3 e6 18. Kh2 Bc6 19. Bg1 Kh8 20.
Rae1 Ng8 21. Nc1 $6 {returning to his original plan;} ({instead,} 21. exf5 $5
Bxg2 22. Nxd4 Bxd4 23. Qxg2 exf5 24. Nd5 {might give White a little something})
