strongest move, in my opinion.} ({In a later game, where Miles had the
chutzpah to repeat this line, he switched to} 7... Qd7 {.} {Instead,} 8. exd6 (
{L.Ljubojevic-A.Miles, European Team Championship, Plovdiv 1983, continued} 8.
Nf3 Nh6 9. exd6 exd6 10. Ne4 Nf5 11. Bg5 O-O 12. O-O f6 13. Bc1 Bb7 14. Bh3
