13. Nxd4 cxd4 14. g4 Ne3 15. Bxe3 dxe3 16. Nxd6 {or} g5 $5 {, intending} (16...
f6 17. Qe2 fxe5 18. Nc4 Qd4 19. fxe5 Rf2 20. Qxe3 Rxf1+ 21. Rxf1 Bxe5 22. Qxd4
Bxd4+ 23. Kh1 Rb8 24. Rb1 {, when it was clear that Black had no issues and
hence 1/2-1/2 B.Spassky-Jo.Horvath, European Cup, Rotterdam 1988.} (24. Z0))
17. Qe2 ({or} 17. d4 e2 $1 18. Qxe2 Qxd4+) 17... gxf4 18. Nc4 Qd4 19. Rac1 Rd8
{with a perfectly good position for Black.}) 11... Nef5 12. Bf2 Nxf3+ 13. Qxf3
({Instead,} 13. Bxf3 dxe5 14. fxe5 Bxe5 15. Ne4 ({not} 15. Na4 $6 Qc7 16. Nxc5
({while after} 16. Bxc5 $2 Bd7 17. Bxf8 {, B.Abramovic-M.Cebalo, Yugoslav
