31... Qf6 32. Qe8 Qe7 33. Qa8 Nc5 34. f5 {Securing the e6-pawn.} ({Taking the
a-pawn was possible:} 34. Qxa5 fxe6 35. Qa2 Kg7 36. dxe6 Qxe6 37. Qd2 {and
