15. Rc1 Ne6 16. Ne3 Qa5 17. exf5 gxf5 18. Nh4 Ned8 19. g4 (19. Nc4 $5 Qa6 20.
Rfe1 {takes the game in a different direction}) 19... fxg4 20. f5 Ne5 21. Nxg4
